  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">w</span> je takođe pravopisni znak. Koristi se kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span> predstavlja glavni samoglasnik u slogu. Pomaže da definiše granice slogova i čini slogove lakšim za čitanje.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Ako se <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span> koristi kao slog, dodajte <span class=\"highlighted-text\">w</span> ispred njega: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">wu</span>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ako silaba počinje sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, promeni u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">w</span>. Primeri: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ua</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">wa</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">uo</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">wo</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">uai</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">wai</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">uei</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">wei</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">uan</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">wan</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ueng</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">weng</span>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">wan</span> u različitim tonomima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">wān</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">弯</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">wán</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">完</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">wǎn</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">晚</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">wàn</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">万</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>",
